{"tid":1417433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[黑色五毛警告]政府已經就快頂唔順，佢地開始急，我地絕對唔可以停","createTime":"2019-08-05T16:34:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T23:11:18.000Z","uid":128705,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0d6c5d2735f419dece16c966ead74cd3136456b2","tid":1417433,"uid":128705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:34:10.000Z","msg":"最近都辛苦哂大家<br />\n你攰我攰大家都攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但如果我地宜家停落黎<br />\n唔單止乜都無<br />\n仲會對唔住所有被捕既手足、犧牲既義士<br />\n一路以黎大家都做得非常好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算係耶穌都要係荒野走四十日啦<br />\n以此我地唔可以放棄，堅持唔一定會好成功<br />\n但我可以講<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">放棄就一定失鳩敗</span><br />\n我地要KEEP住繼續做落去<br />\n唔可以俾班共狗五毛睇死<br />\n<br />\n香港人要繼續<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span><br />\n以上願主保佑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n祝大家旗開得勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26a52853e37c3a5c92bc70289ccd7386975fbc88","tid":1417433,"uid":128705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:45:15.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"4213eb6c5b67a279b59bc8d3ab1e51e013cbde6b","tid":1417433,"uid":128705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:53:06.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"4b8098d39a9e8802043a9aa65f3eeb28fa8f7831","tid":1417433,"uid":128705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:06:54.000Z","msg":"有兩個五毛負皮"},{"pid":"f1b01a47e792b9a35794a19c7a8635994bc9ea59","tid":1417433,"uid":128705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:32:25.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"f72aa22f9104adb1d920d337ebc8c1075ab276c3","tid":1417433,"uid":235754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:35:52.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命！！"},{"pid":"4bda08ca55733842bea1e5227067ab0d6b211355","tid":1417433,"uid":1